Class IntegerComparator

java.lang.Object
  suncertify.db.dao.comparator.IntegerComparator
All Implemented Interfaces:
IComparator
public class IntegerComparator
extends Object
implements IComparator

IntegerComparator is an implementation of comparator that compares string values as integers - it simply converts given strings to integer objects and invokes Integer.compareTo(java.lang.Integer) method.
